title: The most cost-effective 1b1b apartment for subletting
posting_body: ['The best and most cost-effective 1b1b apartment for subletting downtown!', 'August-October 31, renewable', 'Transportation: It takes 8 minutes to get to the UMN by the highway.', 'It is very convenient to go wherever you want.', 'There is a bus stop downstairs, as well as a bicycle stop for lime, Nice ride, Lyft bike, and an EV charging station.', 'neighbourhood: across the street is the community college, science centre and a library, so pretty quiet.', 'The large window of the room faces the Cathedral of Santa Maria.', 'The room faces south, so the sunset scenery is invincible every evening, and every shot is a painting', 'On the edge of Loring park, walk five minutes to the Big Cherry and walk art centre', 'Two-minute walk to the grocery L&B, next to the grocery store are dry cleaners and wineries, as well as barber shops and manicures', 'Walk for two minutes to the cafe and Bar Lurcat, there are several beautiful bridal shops on the side', 'Management Office:', 'Downstairs is the day care, the security is first-class, and nothing has happened for almost a year.', 'Downstairs in the apartment is an amazing pet park that only belongs to the apartment.', 'Good news for friends who have pets!', 'Walk 5 minutes to many amazing restaurants, 10 minutes to union rooftop, 15 minutes to gay 90, and fifteen minutes to target centre.', 'Security is always here and they are all friendly', 'Although it is a semi-indoor parking lot like a hotel, it is really good in a place like downtown where the parking space fee is 250-300.', 'It only cost you $80', 'You can use two swimming pools, two hot tubs, two gyms, a cinema, and many rooms for group study.']
